content:
For a IG that validates, are these the correct URLs for these extensions.... Two have the uv/sdc path and one does not?

http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/sdc/StructureDefinition/sdc-questionnaire-answerExpression

http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/sdc/StructureDefinition/sdc-questionnaire-initialExpression

http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/variable
That's fine. There will be a variety of extension roots. 'variable' isn't specific to SDC or even to Questionnaire.
